  "title": "Two round shiny UFOs sighted flying over Curitiba [2000]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/14/two-round-shiny-ufos-sighted-flying-over-curitiba-2000/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-s3",
  "content": "<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>OCT 22nd, 2000</strong>. Time: 14h20pm. Time: 15 minutes. In downtown Curitiba three people observed two round silver shiny UFOs flying fast at an altitude of 10km and going towards the South region &#8220;near Santa Cândida&#8221;. The UFOs made no noise and left no condensation trails. There were no video recordings or photographs registered. The visibility conditions were good at the time of sighting.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.584. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre avistamento de ovni na Praça Rui Barbosa, cidade de Curitiba, Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>OCT 22nd, 2000. Time: 14h20pm. Time: 15 minutes. In downtown Curitiba three people observed two round silver shiny UFOs flying fast at an altitude of 10km and going towards the South region &#8220;near Santa Cândida&#8221;. The UFOs made no noise and left no condensation trails. There were no video recordings or photographs registered. The visibility [&hellip;]</p>\n",
